---
import {
  H2C,
  H3C,
  Paragraph,
  TextWithLine,
} from '@components/atoms/index.astro'

const { customClass = '' } = Astro.props
---

<header class=`${customClass}`>
  <div
    class='rounded-full lg:rounded-2xl w-40 h-40 lg:w-full lg:h-full sm:w-60 sm:h-60 max-w-xs max-h-xs overflow-hidden mx-auto lg:mx-0 blur-sm hover:blur-none hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105'
  >
    <img class='w-full h-full object-cover' src='/imgs/persona.jpg' alt='Foto de Omar Barros' />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:justify-around gap-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <div class='max-w-max'>
        <H3C customClass='relative text-start w-max'>
          <TextWithLine name='OMAR BARROS' customClass='border-[#333333]' />
        </H3C>
        <H2C customClass='text-blue-600 w-max m-auto lg:font-black lg:text-4xl'>INGENIERO DE SISTEMAS</H2C>
        <H2C customClass='text-blue-600 w-max m-auto lg:font-black lg:text-4xl'>DESARROLLADOR WEB</H2C>
      </div>
  
      <Paragraph customClass='max-w-lg my-2'>
        Uniendo talento técnico, espíritu innovador y dedicación: construyendo
        experiencias web excepcionales que impulsan el éxito
      </Paragraph>
    </div>

    <slot />
  </div>

</header>
